      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> garlic </strong>and<strong> ginger</strong> to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the<strong> ground cumin</strong>, <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>mango chutney</strong> and the<strong> </strong>juice of half your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>mint leaves</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>Hariyali-style marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1600417107083-x200.jpg",
