            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, roughly chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and shred it roughly</p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> in a large bowl and set aside for serving – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p><p>In a separate bowl, combine the juice of the<strong> remaining lemon</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1600417146611-x200.jpg",
