          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1600417195618-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Hariyali-style basa</strong> with any <strong>cooked Hariyali-style marinade </strong>from the pan over the <strong>basmati rice </strong>with the <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and drizzle the salad with the <strong>zingy lemon dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
